summary.short: The customer, Beth, calls Premier Phone Services to cancel her phone plan. The agent, Tom, offers to help cancel the plan and asks Beth about her phone plan and reasons for canceling. Beth expresses dissatisfaction with the graphics on her phone and the poor quality of some games. Tom apologizes and offers to cancel the plan and transfer Beth to another device. They also discuss canceling Beth's plan and confirm her billing address.
